subject: JUnit Software QA job available north of Boston
msgSnippet: Software QA job available north of Boston for growing company.  Client uses Extreme programming methodology and wants QA testers familiar with this framework.
messageBody:
Software QA job available north of Boston for growing company. Client
uses Extreme programming methodology and wants QA testers familiar
with this framework. Background as a developer or Systems Engineer
before moving into QA is a major plus. Both contract and direct hire
(aka perm) jobs available.
